  - MITRE ATT&CK
  - multi-agent defense
  - surgical robotics
abstract: >
  Proof-of-Concept simulation of a Da Vinci-class surgical robot interface
  compromised by Data Poisoning and Ransomware attacks against an integrated
  Medical LLM, defended in real-time by a multi-agent Cyber-Security AI
  architecture. Demonstrates 4 attack scenarios mapped to MITRE ATT&CK.
  Multilingual support (EN/FR/PT).
